reviewText:
This DVD is probably one of a kind about the Santa Fe -- especially the footage about the last run on the Santa Fe Branch.  But it lacks a lot in video coverage of some of the most beautiful parts of the Santa Fe - such as the area around Raton Pass.  The video coverage wastes a lot of time on street train coverage and doesn't cover some of the areas that are more interesting -- for example, Kansas City.

Twila
